<topic id="switching-between-open-tabs">
  <title>Switching Between Opened Tabs</title><prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords><indexterm>Switch tabs</indexterm></keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>There are two keyboard shortcuts that can be used for cycling through the opened file
      tabs:</p>
    <p>
      <dl>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol conkeyref="reusable_oxygen_shortcuts_list/ctrl_tab"/></dt>
          <dd>Switches between the tabs with opened files in the order most recent ones first.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol conkeyref="reusable_oxygen_shortcuts_list/ctrl_shift_tab"/></dt>
          <dd>Switches between the tabs with opened files in the reverse order.</dd>
        </dlentry>
      </dl>
    </p>
  </body>
